data.description: This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bath home is located on a spacious corner lot in the highly desirable Northwood neighborhood of Edmond. The home has been recently updated with new carpet in the bedrooms, new wood laminate down the hallway, a new primary shower and plumbing, fresh paint throughout, and all plumbing under the sinks has been redone. The HVAC has also been recently cleaned and serviced. The backyard is an entertainer's dream with an open back patio and mature landscaping. The newer fence provides privacy and security for you. This home is conveniently located near Kilpatrick Turnpike, restaurants, shopping, and schools. It is also within walking distance to Smiling Hill, which features a playground, walking trails, and a pond. Don't miss out on this opportunity to own a beautiful corner lot home in a great Edmond neighborhood! Schedule a showing today!
